tonight:
As president-elect Trump expands
his team

00:10.711 --> 00:16.783 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
with new picks, we talk to
Republican Party
spokesman Sean Spicer and look
at how the

00:16.817 --> 00:19.152 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
