being redefined.

00:19.186 --> 00:23.957 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Also ahead
this Wednesday:
Rescuers search under the rubble
for survivors

00:23.991 --> 00:29.329 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
