after a powerful
earthquake kills nearly 100
people.

00:29.363 --> 00:32.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And when religion
and art collide.

00:32.766 --> 00:37.771 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
