celebrates the beauty
and mastery of the Qur'an.

00:37.804 --> 00:39.606 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MASSUMEH FARHAD, Chief Curator,
Arthur M.
Sackler Gallery, Smithsonian
Institution:

00:39.640 --> 00:45.512 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It really shifted my perception
of what these
works are, and I'm hoping that
it will also

00:45.545 --> 00:49.950 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
shift the perception of the
visitors who come
to the museum to see the
exhibition.

00:49.983 --> 00:52.686 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: All that and
more on tonight's
"PBS NewsHour."

00:52.719 --> 00:56.957 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
