00:56.990 --> 01:08.936 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: A new flurry
of high-level
announcements today from the
Trump transition.

01:08.969 --> 01:13.407 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They include a new ambassador
and a new leader
for small business interests,
and the incoming

01:13.440 --> 01:16.176 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
