01:18.078 --> 01:21.915 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: He didn't
appear in New York's
Trump Tower lobby today, but
president-elect

01:21.949 --> 01:28.021 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Donald Trump still made
headlines, as "TIME"
magazine named him its 2016
person of the

01:28.055 --> 01:31.959 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
