serving female
senator ever.

08:11.424 --> 08:13.193 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

08:13.226 --> 08:15.695 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARBARA MIKULSKI (D), Maryland:
