soared today on
mounting expectations of faster
growth.

08:44.190 --> 08:49.963 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Dow Jones industrial average
reached another
record, gaining nearly 300
points to close

08:49.996 --> 08:52.465 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
at 19549.

