the S&amp;P 500
added 29, for its own record
close.

08:58.905 --> 09:02.809 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And thousands
of people
converged on Pearl Harbor today,
marking 75

09:02.842 --> 09:07.113 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
years since the Japanese attack
that brought
the United States into World War
II.

09:07.147 --> 09:11.584 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Elderly survivors highlighted
the crowd that
gathered across the harbor from
where the

09:11.618 --> 09:13.353 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
