09:13.386 --> 09:17.090 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They observed a moment of
silence and then
listened to tributes to all
those killed on

09:17.123 --> 09:18.958 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
